{"tid":903021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希特拉與猶太小女孩慶生日結緣 相擁照片以9萬元成交","createTime":"2018-11-15T08:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T15:33:10.000Z","uid":75969,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fc352b8dbb8be73107ee4495b3d592dbfbeedaed","tid":903021,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:53:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/resizer/TwWNhto-veVBgaC0fdK3UEIO44A=/1484x0/arc-anglerfish-washpost-prod-washpost.s3.amazonaws.com/public/AHHBJJXHOEI6RBCJD7ZGGYE2GE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fresizer%2FTwWNhto-veVBgaC0fdK3UEIO44A%3D%2F1484x0%2Farc-anglerfish-washpost-prod-washpost.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2FAHHBJJXHOEI6RBCJD7ZGGYE2GE.jpg&h=df513c37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n德國納粹狂魔希特拉二戰期間對猶太人進行「大屠殺」，但原來他憐愛一名有猶太人血統的小女孩。美國馬里蘭州的亞歷山大歷史拍賣行周二拍賣一張黑白照片，相片中希特拉輕著一名小女孩，最終以11,520美元(約9萬港元)成交。<br />\n<br />\n照片中的希特拉面露笑容，彎身輕摟著當時6歲的小女孩尼瑙(Rosa Bernile Nienau)。據報，這張照片是霍夫曼(Heinrich Hoffmann)在1933年拍下，之後希特拉曾廣泛使用這張照片，宣傳他的仁慈形像。<br />\n<br />\n有研究指，希特拉雖然知道小女孩的祖母是猶太人，但也無礙二人成「好友」。根據威爾遜(James Wilson)所著《特希拉的阿爾卑斯總部》(Hitler's Alpine Headquarters)一書，提及希特拉一名心腹發現女孩有猶太人血統後，擅自禁止她與她母親到訪希特拉退守之地，最後令希特拉感到不開心。<br />\n<br />\n據報，希特拉與該名小女孩相遇在希特拉某年生日當天。當日，希特拉在一處館內慶生日，剛好得知附近有一名和他同日出生的女孩在慶祝，於是邀請她和他合照，此後，二人不時有見面和通信。至幾年後，該名女孩因病逝世。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/865366\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F865366&d=XciyCYDR5ar%2FqBRqMlYw98PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=4b94d1e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F865366&h=738fb05b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/865366</a>"},{"pid":"0f6281ebe0d230fc358dcd3c0df7b96103ee5b29","tid":903021,"uid":79793,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:56:55.000Z","msg":"影得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9829204920c6b2589f7d934fe3b84e5f95a60e","tid":903021,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18815ab62ea5ed4b46cf8b51f96bbb1cf5982858","tid":903021,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be01e08b8b45ca69ec6abf6d91d72c6a85d39ac","tid":903021,"uid":81183,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"至幾年後，該名女孩因病逝世。<br />\n<br />\n定係比人發現左掉左入去集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df1441aaa30d0bbe291280c0238b02eb9d4a35a","tid":903021,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:22:49.000Z","msg":"幼幼"},{"pid":"ebdac8563eac765cfc6ad91881ee4b67861c2cab","tid":903021,"uid":37856,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:32:56.000Z","msg":"阿銀：點解你要呃我？<br />\n達叔：大佬呀，&ldquo;希特拉與猶太小女孩相擁&rdquo;呢下嘢你都信嘅？咁唔呃你呃邊個呀？你教我喇，唔該。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLdWKZn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLdWKZn.png&h=8e061f6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad5c8b8f19c796af2278e756e8ed928746df0d56","tid":903021,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebdac8563eac765cfc6ad91881ee4b67861c2cab","tid":903021,"uid":37856,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:32:56.000Z","msg":"阿銀：點解你要呃我？<br />\n達叔：大佬呀，&ldquo;希特拉與猶太小女孩相擁&rdquo;呢下嘢你都信嘅？咁唔呃你呃邊個呀？你教我喇，唔該。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLdWKZn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLdWKZn.png&h=8e061f6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201